1.000000 2014-07-14T20:00:31Z
 [00 Major]
 - Packaging changes that may break downstreams that work by hand.
 - Internals and stylistic tweaks.

 [01 New Version Scheme]
 - Moving to x.yyyyyy instead of x.y.z ( https://questhub.io/realm/perl/quest/5388d3a9bbd0be2224000129 )
 - This is the primary reason for the 1.0 on the box.

 [02 New Toolkit]
 - This release ships with EUMM instead of MB ( https://questhub.io/realm/perl/quest/5388cc12bbd0be5b2500011f )
 - "latest" Toolkit dependencies softened to "recommends" instead of "requires"

